    <description>
        <en><![CDATA[1 Unreal Modpack.
This is a bunch of base game vehicles (plus some mods from GIANTS) with various options added. More color configurations, unreal capacities, high-speed motors and transmissions, faster working speeds, wider working widths, color configurations, and more. Please read changelog (included, Discord server also) for all compatibilities and features. Not all vehicles and configurations are real.
I hope you enjoy.

Please use official download link only!
https://github.com/DORF1010/FS25_1_Unreal_Modpack

Any questions, comments, concerns, suggestions, please contact me via Discord
https://discord.gg/XVErHTQgms
(My Discord server)

GIANTS unlimited color configuration mod is highly suggested, so it is linked as a dependency.]]>
		</en>
	</description>
